Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to discuss today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, who's going to be number uno?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Numero uno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hippity hop, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sign that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could speak briefly about what the significance is of Lucifer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in particular as related from theosophy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that there are some interpretations that the fall or descent was actually a beneficial thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he know it's beneficial?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've never come across that interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's the fall, we should thank Lucifer for our fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For his fall, for sacrificing his place in heaven, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Evidently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he wouldn't be Lucifer, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If he sacrificed himself for us, he'd be Saint Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some little gifts for your animals and for you guys, some chocolates and some
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,doggie bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned in the beginning that you had a bird, a dog, and three cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we got bird treats, cat toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know the size of the dog, so we just got these bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli for broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have broccoli, we got you broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's for broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know you love chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We love chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't know what kind, so we got you from hazelnut to white to dark to coconut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gracious me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And a pen to write more books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And a pen for each direct book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A lioness for Susan and a little cute piggy for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To write those books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:02:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if you could bless this for me and if I could just shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless this lovely necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And could you bless my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lindsay, Brittany, Joshua, and Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How about your new car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to bless that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold them in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, we ask for blessings on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The beloveds that are being held in our mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to see you both again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are like blue diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I love both of you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And through the grace of God, through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for you, I'd still be sticking needles in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd still be living on the street and going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of you, I have a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just, I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:03:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you and God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the reason for addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol or drugs, is that, you remember that scale of consciousness goes from the highest to the lowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the drug or the alcohol suppresses all the lower levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, it allows only, you experience only the higher ones because the lower ones have been suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's not coming from the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that that's the way you would be in a more advanced state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what the drug does is suppress negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And it allows you to feel elation and happiness and joy, which is what you should be experiencing all the time anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is through spiritual endeavor, you reach those higher states of consciousness without the aid, without having to suppress or depress the lower feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the purpose of the 12 steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of resentments, live one day at a time, and stay with the group spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say thanks, first of all, so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, I'm still having a really hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about it so much in previous lectures, but integrating spirituality with, like, work and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I still, I don't know, it probably just takes time, but, like, I really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know if I understand, but I appreciate the profundity of the lectures and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still have, like, a desire for, like, lots of money and stuff like that that I can't seem to shake off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so much that, but just, like, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just, like, success, sort of, in material.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was going to give you lots of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, I used to live on Millionaire's Row, and those people shot themselves with the same frequency as people in the poverty section of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So happiness, then, has nothing to do with material possessions, because even if it was material possessions, what you're experiencing is the joy of accomplishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which is non-material.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-physical, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I might get a picture, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you've got a lot of money, you can't live in subsidized housing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a student, the county had subsidized housing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived there for $15 a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bedrooms, $15 a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was on the GI Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you signed that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, first, I just wanted to express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That you elect to stay here and be our teacher and guide and to your support staff who makes all this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if I could hold someone in my mind, if you could tell me if they are an accurate muscle tester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If they can accurately...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a muscle test to see if the person you're holding in town is a muscle tester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how accurate it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ask the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what she's asking possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you got the person in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask about the person she's holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is an adequate muscle tester.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they get...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes when you first start out doing muscle testing, you sometimes get higher figures than what you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first start out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first start out doing the muscle testing, you sometimes get a little bit higher calibration or figure than what you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's easy to do because you want the best for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a common thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, sometimes you're not right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But could I be the weak link in this test because I'm holding them in mind and I might not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never done that before, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't know if that was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to test them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The testing technique itself, you know, we'd have to do a whole lecture on that again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very, very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet people screw it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how they screw it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that purity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,People can't resist putting their intention on a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's rare that people can just be objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what they want, they want a certain answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they're trying to prove that that answer is true because they want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to be detached has to be scientific.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not sure I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Scientific detachment means you don't care how many molecules there is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the computer figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you've got to be detached like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I find most people are not that detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the reason they're asking the question to begin with is because they're not detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, this stock is going to go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason they want to know that is because they own a bunch of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, I'm having a lot of trouble letting go of my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgmentalism and my spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting go of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:10:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging of everything and it's constant commentary going on all the time and I don't know how to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing to do is let go of it from your perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, what you don't think is correct or right or something maybe just right for the other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You see somebody angry and expressive and now you think they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that person spent three years in psychoanalysis learning how to be aggressive and assertive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the first time I told somebody to F off and gave them the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was jubilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy as a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy as a lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could sign my course book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cookbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My spiritual cookbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a neat cover you have on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember the first time I gave somebody the finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just jubilant that I was so assertive and aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, I was always afraid of offending somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to breathe in and out for fear I would offend somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, this is a book you must read.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at his tatters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could sign that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he has a white sharpie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good looking guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My question was about, are you familiar with the Self-Realization Fellowship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about their lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the Self-Realization Fellowship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, you're not familiar with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yucca Nauticus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yucca Nauticus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yucca Nauticus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote the autobiography?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not familiar with it as an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me about an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Self-Realization Fellowship organization is what you're asking me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think the last time I went near that, it's in the high 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-Realization 500 is over 580, 575.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,570.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-Realization Fellowship is over 565.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the high 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,565.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Yogananda's teachings himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The founder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yogananda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yogananda's teachings itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the list up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like 570, 575, 580, 590, 585.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Supercalifragilisticexpialidocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty high then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nice meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Autobiography of a yogi it's what he's asking me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Been so many years, I forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you that I love you very much and I'm really happy to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan, for sharing the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had something similar happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lying in bed and I was waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This light came.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it was like coming from within me and it came up and it just lit out the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,room yes and it was like I felt like I couldn't breathe that's it and I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,know if that was the self like the big self you didn't know if it was what well
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't the small one was it but just you sharing your experience yes that's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of the presence of God itself with a capital S okay thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,very much could I just touch your hand yes thank you well all day I was very
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,teary and just like I felt like I couldn't function I was just crying a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,lot but I was happy yeah and nothing has come close since like absolutely
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing about ten seconds that was it and just you sharing that just brought
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it up within me today so fine yeah I'm getting an echo here it's hard to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the person speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,pick one yes yeah I have a question uh but uh the constitution you said was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,700 and what is 700 the constitution so I may have to repeat okay yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,constitution of states of America yeah the second amendment all manner to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,create arms is being you know uh people are for guns and against guns and uh I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a retired policeman and I've always carried a gun and I wondered you know it seems like from the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,from my point of view, that the freedom of the country
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is important for people to be able to bear arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know, because there's so many people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,seem to be against guns, which position is more true
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,or right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, from what position?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The right to bear arms, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just, we have permission to calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 450, 480, 500, 490, 495, it calibrates around 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, that would be intellectually correct
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and certainly would fit into the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Founding Fathers, that we should have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:18:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,all the freedoms possible, except when to do so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,would put others at grave risk or cause them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to lose their freedom, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be my readout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put a link on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a lot of years since I packed that .45.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Navy would stand watch, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we were in the South Pacific, you didn't have to wear
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,many clothes, it was so hot, so I'd be on night watch
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,totaled to four or something, and all you had on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,was your shorts and your duty belt with a loaded .45
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,caliber and your holster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A holster and your holster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And your holster and your shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my question is regarding demonic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanna know what the first step
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in eliminating that kind of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it influences my actions and how to get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you lead a pure life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you lead a pure life, the negative energies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,will leave you because you become distasteful to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what you do is lead a pure life yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround yourself with positive, pure energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Associate with people that are spiritually advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out with spiritual groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing demons hate worse than angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out with angels and the demons will leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Flies always hang around garbage, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you lead as pure a life as you can yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Demons don't like spirituality and purity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask if the person on that card
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,can accurately answer questions
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,through muscle testing with a pendulum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't work with the pendulums and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all different energy of, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well can muscle testing be done with a pendulum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Like-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just do muscle testing with muscle testing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and pendulums with pendulums?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to mix them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the same thing exact,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not called muscle testing, or-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pendulum is one thing, muscle testing is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're both accurate,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you should get the same answers both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Оokay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,answer both ways can I ask one more question how do you recognize demonic energy and like yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or your friends or whatever like if like if you're questioning whether you or your friends are
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,possessed you know by demons how could you recognize oh I wouldn't play with that game
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you could use the same as you do with any other you know I'd say this person is possessed by evil
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,demons yes or no or if you use the pendulum also your intuition your spiritual intuition should
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,tell you although some are very sophisticated in the way they present themselves some come on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:22:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,very holy in fact when people come on super holy I'm always suspicious of them if you're so holy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to do the whole like you're a movie movie holy person you know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just integrous because that's who you are so there's no need to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,love you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lay it on people you know two-foot-high crucifixes a foot across and long robes and the sandals and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the Jesus haircut you know forget all that okay thank you can I ask if you know this person
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:23:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,yes you talk about giving people a shot of love what
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,found is that sometimes you'll give people a shot of love and out of the blue all of a sudden you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,give them an overdose in which case they will either start crying and come up and give you a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,hug or they go into a panic their eyes get big and they went to a panic and they will avoid you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is there any way that you can learn how to give them let's say five CC's instead of ten thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,CC's don't give or receive love it's not a commodity just be a part of it and it's not a commodity just
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,be what you are period just be what you are walk around the beetle rather than squish them you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:24:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,have to lean lean over and kiss them scare the beetle if you try to kiss it yeah now if you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.41,0:24:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,respect the integrity of others and treat them integrously that that is loving to treat people
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,integrously to begin with yes you just tore my ear off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love your laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love your laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love your laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I love your laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.17,0:24:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for being here Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is I teach yoga in an adolescent psych ward and in the prison system for teens
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.17,0:24:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You teach yoga where?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.17,0:24:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the prison system for teenagers and in the children in psych wards at a children's hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.58,0:24:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and what would be my best approach with them because a lot of them are brilliant children
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:24:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are really what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.76,0:24:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are brilliant children
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.76,0:24:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.82,0:25:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can I do to help get them to the next place of health mental health?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.79,0:25:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I can't answer it the way you're presenting it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.79,0:25:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about yoga that's one thing mental health is another
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.20,0:25:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know people who do yoga right and left for you know years in their careers they're in a loon
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.51,0:25:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't so crazy they wouldn't be doing yoga around the clock for years in and years out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.89,0:25:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoga is good if you're going to be a dance teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.89,0:25:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some physical things that I can help them with with their bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.00,0:25:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're not in their bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.00,0:25:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's not using their bodies right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.00,0:26:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not in their bodies you know the mentally handicapped are not in their bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.00,0:26:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.00,0:26:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to be doing with them teaching them yoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.00,0:26:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing I'm doing yoga with them but the thing that they absolutely love is relaxation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the relaxation it gets them to the next place
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it are you hired as a therapist or yoga teacher or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoga teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.00,0:26:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A yoga teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.00,0:26:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.00,0:26:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright so why don't you just teach them yoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.00,0:26:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well she's saying in the relaxation and the cool down there's certain terms that you talk about to relax them after they've had this whole
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.55,0:26:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well whatever if that's the yoga then you do the yoga
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.55,0:26:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you could maybe inspire them with wonderful thoughts is what I would say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.48,0:26:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe that would take advantage of that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.48,0:26:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You could take beautiful thoughts rather than where their mind has been
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.48,0:26:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.48,0:26:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That might help
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.67,0:26:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay great
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.66,0:27:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know like a thought like that God loves you all the time no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.17,0:27:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or anything like that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.17,0:27:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.17,0:27:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that would help you know if you say that in a certain way you know without mentioning God
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.17,0:27:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It can still be an uplifting experience in a cool down
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.17,0:27:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.17,0:27:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I just tell people you're lovable just as you are you don't have to be any different for God to love you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.23,0:27:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome great I will thank you thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.34,0:28:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.34,0:28:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.34,0:28:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.22,0:28:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping things simple answers most questions
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.22,0:28:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.68,0:28:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to teach them yoga then just teach them yoga
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.68,0:28:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.89,0:28:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.89,0:28:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.89,0:28:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello it's nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.05,0:28:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to ask you what is the soul in relation to the one self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.53,0:28:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul is the self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.53,0:28:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are many souls
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.53,0:28:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.53,0:28:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And only one self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.53,0:28:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean there's many souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.53,0:28:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have multiple souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.53,0:28:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.53,0:28:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope not
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.92,0:28:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No when he says self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.92,0:28:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Self with a capital S that is the higher self
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.95,0:29:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher self and then there's self with a small s that's the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.95,0:29:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.49,0:29:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of A Course in Miracles when it said that there's only one son of God
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.49,0:29:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it splits into many egos and there are many souls
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.88,0:29:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I can't put it together
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.88,0:29:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't put it together
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.88,0:29:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a breakdown in the language
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.62,0:29:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The languaging oh yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the languaging
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.48,0:29:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the workbook or the textbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's German so it's a breakdown in language
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.61,0:29:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the textbook or the workbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.61,0:29:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.76,0:29:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes the textbook calibrates less than the workbook for this very reason
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.76,0:29:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The workbook calibrates to 600 the textbook calibrates 550
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.36,0:29:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.36,0:30:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is this hypothetical languaging
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.65,0:30:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiential reality is not the way it's languaged in that book
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.39,0:30:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.52,0:30:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.52,0:30:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah the workbook is much harder than that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.52,0:30:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one self with a capital S which is divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.80,0:30:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So divinity cannot be multiple it's one
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.83,0:30:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the multiple is the expression of the one
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.83,0:30:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.66,0:30:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't need to understand it intellectually anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.66,0:30:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is only one soul
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.66,0:30:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.66,0:30:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one soul that we share together?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.88,0:30:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.88,0:30:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one soul within you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.88,0:30:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.17,0:30:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.17,0:30:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.33,0:30:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.62,0:30:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one self with a capital S and that is the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.62,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.62,0:30:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God is each one is experiencing it as the self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.76,0:31:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is only one divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.76,0:31:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.60,0:31:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one experiences it as the presence of divinity within
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.60,0:31:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one sunshine shining
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.20,0:31:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person experiences the radiance of the sun somewhat differently
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.00,0:31:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean they are different suns
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.00,0:31:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means each one is experiencing the sun from their own perceptual intellectual level
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.57,0:31:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.57,0:31:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.57,0:31:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.57,0:31:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.57,0:31:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It clarifies it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.76,0:31:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.42,0:31:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You go six inches this way for the camera
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.42,0:31:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.42,0:31:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You go six inches this way
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.42,0:31:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Six inches?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.42,0:31:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.42,0:31:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God man
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.42,0:31:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you want a foot
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.42,0:31:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.67,0:31:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,First they ask six inches then they want a foot
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.67,0:31:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.67,0:31:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.50,0:31:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your arm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.50,0:31:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your legs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.60,0:32:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.60,0:32:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.23,0:32:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.96,0:32:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If it ain't one thing it's the other
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.96,0:32:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.96,0:32:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.15,0:32:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.43,0:32:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you to bless this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.43,0:32:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd just like to express gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.96,0:32:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.96,0:32:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.08,0:32:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.47,0:32:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.33,0:32:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to bless it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.57,0:32:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.09,0:32:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to bless this Buddha and resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.38,0:32:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.21,0:32:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.51,0:32:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.95,0:32:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.77,0:32:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.68,0:32:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just want to express gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.82,0:32:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.48,0:33:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, first of all, I want to say thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.20,0:33:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question on guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.25,0:33:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you transcend experience when you experientially feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.52,0:33:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak slow and near the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.63,0:33:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When there is experience that you have intentionally gone against the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.83,0:33:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you transcend the guilt from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.03,0:33:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The echoes are bearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.69,0:33:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When you intentionally go against the self, and you know you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you transcend that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.26,0:33:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she feels guilt over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.34,0:34:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.16,0:34:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to forgive yourself and decide to do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.93,0:34:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.67,0:34:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.15,0:34:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.11,0:34:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide that you're only human, and human does the best it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.25,0:34:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not perfect in its expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.92,0:34:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're tolerant and benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.17,0:34:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a benign attitude towards your own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.85,0:34:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.79,0:34:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to ask you if you could expound more on surrendering the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.51,0:34:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,attachment to self-sabotage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.05,0:34:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.95,0:34:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-sabotage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.31,0:34:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.03,0:34:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The surrendering attachment to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.45,0:34:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.61,0:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.11,0:35:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by self-sabotage?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.73,0:35:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the ego's...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.17,0:35:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the ego's always trying to freeze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.80,0:35:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lack of perfection?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.02,0:35:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Error?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.16,0:35:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.64,0:35:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like nothing's ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.43,0:35:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously nothing's ever good enough for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.37,0:35:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.13,0:35:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to surrender the programming behind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.31,0:35:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hear what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.83,0:35:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The programming behind what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.19,0:35:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfection?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.71,0:35:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.75,0:35:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's carrying shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.23,0:35:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.49,0:35:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know how does he overcome shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.69,0:35:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he should be ashamed of feeling shame all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.23,0:35:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You accept the fact that you're only immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.93,0:36:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you're prone to error.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.44,0:36:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And yes, forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.74,0:36:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you pray to do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.81,0:36:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.44,0:36:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's almost impossible to live in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and not regret some action, be ashamed of some action.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.06,0:36:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you forgive yourself that it's just part of being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.70,0:36:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the reason we're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.30,0:36:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is to overcome these defects of character
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.58,0:36:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and transcend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.04,0:36:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.48,0:36:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to be benign towards yourself as well as others.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.74,0:36:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See, so it's not only to stop being judgmental towards others,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.60,0:36:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but to stop being judgmental about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.98,0:36:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, you know, out of wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.62,0:36:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you decide you won't go in that direction anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.28,0:37:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But you accord yourself the same forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.24,0:37:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.83,0:37:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone else did that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.09,0:37:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be willing to forgive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.49,0:37:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.11,0:37:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're willing to forgive them,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.77,0:37:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then you forgive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.58,0:37:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For being stupid and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.00,0:37:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.29,0:37:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You accord yourself the same forgiveness you would
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.33,0:37:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to your brother, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.90,0:37:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And say, look, he's an imperfect human.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.72,0:37:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's doing the best he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.49,0:37:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.05,0:37:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We give them in Christ's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.98,0:37:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And ask God to help us do better next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.31,0:37:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.35,0:38:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I first want to shake your hand and her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.09,0:38:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.75,0:38:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.19,0:38:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak slowly, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.45,0:38:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I first want to shake your hand and her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.75,0:38:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.16,0:38:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.06,0:38:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or touch your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.37,0:38:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.43,0:38:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.32,0:38:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having really bad audio feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.38,0:38:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is a sign already.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.78,0:38:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, what is the purpose of a mediator?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.24,0:38:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to concentrate on what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.38,0:38:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.96,0:38:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the purpose of a mediator in what regard?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.10,0:38:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sense of Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.90,0:38:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ or Buddha or Krishna?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.42,0:38:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.38,0:38:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The ordinary mortal would not have the temerity to address divinity directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.62,0:38:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, Jesus Christ, or an aspect of the Buddha,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.59,0:39:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,acts in your behalf as your advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.82,0:39:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleads your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.84,0:39:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So for Christians, Jesus Christ will say to God
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.70,0:39:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is one of my flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.21,0:39:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have taught him, and I will be looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.99,0:39:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be answerable for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.08,0:39:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you screw up, Jesus goes to God about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.42,0:39:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.52,0:39:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.18,0:39:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there is also a similar representation of Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.62,0:39:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In Lotusland Buddhism,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.40,0:39:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Vala Katsavara is that aspect of the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.72,0:39:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that will speak in your behalf before the ultimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.52,0:39:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.14,0:39:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.04,0:39:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.45,0:39:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you pray to Jesus Christ as Savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.51,0:39:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,how does he save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:40:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He speaks for you before the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.55,0:40:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.53,0:40:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.82,0:40:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.66,0:40:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a lawyer guarantees to the court
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.79,0:40:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will come up with the fine next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.17,0:40:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.42,0:40:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both very much, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.13,0:40:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.25,0:40:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.27,0:40:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.29,0:40:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.33,0:40:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.39,0:40:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.49,0:40:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.67,0:40:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.69,0:40:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.79,0:40:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.85,0:40:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.87,0:40:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.01,0:40:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.05,0:40:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.11,0:40:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.59,0:40:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.59,0:40:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The following question is submitted by Rob Corr
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.19,0:40:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,from the consciousnessproject.org.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.15,0:40:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When we go through the process of enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.09,0:40:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for example, leaving the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.31,0:40:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,losing interest in worldly things, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.09,0:40:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,will it be something we realize why it's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.87,0:40:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it occurs to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.49,0:40:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, I'm losing interest in worldly involvement,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.93,0:40:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is that an ego trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.54,0:40:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.94,0:41:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one indication.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.66,0:41:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have less and less interest in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.26,0:41:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the values of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.02,0:41:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And spiritual values become predominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.09,0:41:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fact that you can make money at something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.49,0:41:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is interesting, but it's not sufficiently interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.22,0:41:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to change your lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.12,0:41:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I could make more money practicing medicine right now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.60,0:41:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,than sitting here talking to you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.70,0:41:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.52,0:41:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.10,0:41:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.60,0:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.18,0:41:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.20,0:41:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, you know, you did that then and you do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.58,0:41:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.12,0:41:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's suitable for one phase of life
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.74,0:41:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,may not be suitable for another.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.22,0:41:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a phase of life where you should be out there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.78,0:41:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,working your butt off to, you know, pay for everything and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.43,0:41:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then once you've accomplished that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.47,0:41:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize I can do that anytime,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.99,0:41:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,then you may move on to the next level, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.89,0:41:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're doing may be right for a certain time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.05,0:42:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of your life, but not at another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.03,0:42:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.81,0:42:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.27,0:42:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.27,0:42:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel Lewis sends her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.27,0:42:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.27,0:42:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.30,0:42:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, is there any place that God is not?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.69,0:42:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any place that God is not?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.69,0:42:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.69,0:42:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.69,0:42:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.69,0:42:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both for the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.69,0:42:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.69,0:42:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just remember they're all your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.69,0:42:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.72,0:42:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Greg Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.72,0:42:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Greg Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.31,0:42:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.31,0:42:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.80,0:42:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.80,0:42:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.24,0:42:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.24,0:42:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.24,0:43:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.77,0:43:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.77,0:43:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.77,0:43:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.77,0:43:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.90,0:43:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.90,0:43:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.99,0:43:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.99,0:43:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.99,0:43:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.99,0:43:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't answer for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.99,0:43:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.99,0:43:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.99,0:43:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.99,0:43:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.02,0:43:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.11,0:43:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wondered if I could shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.11,0:43:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.11,0:43:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.78,0:43:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming up and saying hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.78,0:43:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.78,0:43:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight to the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.78,0:43:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.78,0:43:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,About a year and a half ago at one of your presentations was almost an off-the-cuff when
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.02,0:43:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you commented that...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.28,0:43:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,at the moment of our birth, the moment of our death is already established. Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.25,0:44:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,recall? The moment of your birth, the moment of your death is established. It's set. It's set. Yes. Could you elaborate on that? No. Oh. What more is there to say? Okay, can I put it into some context? No. Okay. You're asking
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.67,0:44:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,an abstract question. Is the moment of your death already preset? Okay. We have permission to ask this. Resist. The answer is yes. Resist. Well, may we conclude then from that? I accept that. You've already got the answer. Now, what is the question? Then health care just makes our life more pleasant. You're dealing with the hypothetical. You see, you're manufacturing a hypothetical rhetorical question with no reality. When you do, it'll leave. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.60,0:45:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be in a car wreck. Yeah. It could be all these other things. So health care is a waste of taxpayers' money because if you're going to croak, you're going to croak. Bye. That's the answer to my question. Hey, we finally got some sound. Thank you. Yeah, I say they're wasting money on these old guys. Their old crocs are going to go anyway. What the hell are you keeping them alive for? The longer they stay alive, the more it costs the taxpayer and Social Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.45,0:45:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question. Yeah, we love your laughter so much. And I think you are the cutest and sweetest person in the world. Oh, my goodness. Can I have your hand? Yes. Yes. She's so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.76,0:46:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say just thank you for being what you are. And I love you. And I need all the help I can get and.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.18,0:46:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just I'm very appreciative. Thank you very much. Yes. Hi. I have a question about resistance. I find that to move from one level to the other, I encounter an awful lot of resistance to doing the things I need to do that I know I need to do. And yet quite often I don't do them. Oh, do it some other lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.23,0:46:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon? Do it some other lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.44,0:47:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you. Thank you very much. That's not good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.32,0:47:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a mean old crab or what? Sometimes. You want him to change, right? Well, I think he wants to. No, I'm asking you. You want him to change, don't you? I see it all over your face. Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.44,0:47:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.84,0:47:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to make her happy, would you be willing to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.10,0:47:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.80,0:47:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.10,0:47:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's working in that direction, at least you know he's trying, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.88,0:47:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.05,0:47:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is somewhat different.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.09,0:47:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if you'd share your thoughts about the atrocities in Rwanda around 1994.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.69,0:47:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something you would comment on?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.01,0:47:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.05,0:47:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.87,0:47:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The atrocities in Rwanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.37,0:47:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rwanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.15,0:48:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where they took out all those people, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.57,0:48:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.29,0:48:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.93,0:48:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a genocide.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.01,0:48:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a genocide, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.63,0:48:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, too much that your comments on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.79,0:48:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.45,0:48:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.53,0:48:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Genocide, well, in a general way, collective karma, there's collective karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.39,0:48:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A country, a community, an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.04,0:48:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jointly agrees to take certain behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.41,0:48:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that's in a negative direction, now they're karmically in debt, are they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.36,0:48:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they come back, and this time they experience a volcano, and it blows 3,000 people, all the smithers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.68,0:48:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.40,0:48:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll ask the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.82,0:48:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is such a thing as group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.86,0:48:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.85,0:48:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.17,0:48:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we know that, but they were asking the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.23,0:48:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's group karma, where everybody agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.28,0:48:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.98,0:48:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In total agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.95,0:49:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's a certain spiritual cost to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.40,0:49:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to undo that, the person may then come back in this lifetime and undo the karma, karmic debt they owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.78,0:49:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were one of those who persecuted and killed the Jews during World War II, you may have a certain karmic debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.89,0:49:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And may come back and yourself, perhaps, be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.58,0:49:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your ethnic origin, or religion, or race, or something, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.98,0:49:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people are always saying, how do all those innocent people, blah, blah, blah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.64,0:49:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always say, they aren't all innocent, or they wouldn't have been, you know, hot lava rained on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.78,0:49:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.50,0:49:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they were turned into ashes in 18 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.52,0:50:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot lava, you know, is at 3,000 degrees, will turn you into ashes in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.56,0:50:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.37,0:50:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's not just accidental that there is a pattern, a karmic pattern, in death and disaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.66,0:50:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and why certain groups always happen to be right where the disasters are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.18,0:50:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they always right where a tsunami is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.04,0:50:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you on Jones Beach, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.18,0:50:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.33,0:50:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.07,0:50:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.42,0:50:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a group, group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.08,0:50:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.50,0:50:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you align yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.34,0:50:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you take on, you take on some of the karmic consequences of that with which you align yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.70,0:50:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.02,0:50:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.05,0:51:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.41,0:51:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is around physical conditions in the body, specifically diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.49,0:51:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something that can be, I guess, cured, or can you actually complete the karma of it in this life, or in the body in this lifetime, and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.04,0:51:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in and of itself, it has no specific karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.20,0:51:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no karmic pattern that, you know, comes forth just as diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.73,0:51:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's generally more genetic than anything else, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.33,0:51:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.03,0:51:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.86,0:51:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, you do everything you can to transcend it using all the modalities that are available in today's world,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.06,0:51:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which were not available, you know, decades ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.36,0:51:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.75,0:51:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.59,0:51:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.98,0:51:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for the work, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.84,0:51:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so, it touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.06,0:51:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.64,0:51:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question has to do with my own purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.14,0:51:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With your own what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.98,0:51:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.76,0:52:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.40,0:52:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.64,0:52:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a landscaping company for 10 years, and I've been called to begin doing spiritual, like, healing work.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.30,0:52:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've started that school, and my heart feels like it's just overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.05,0:52:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll get spontaneous pains and so forth in my body, and then they'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.13,0:52:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.55,0:52:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm called to that work, and there's such a divinity with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.42,0:52:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like I still have responsibilities to these other things that I've created in my landscaping business and my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.22,0:52:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, there's just such a part of me I could just let it go, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.76,0:52:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And, okay, bankruptcy, fine, whatever, you know, let it all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.52,0:52:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think there's some fear there around, you know, perhaps even the karmic consequences of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.08,0:52:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic consequences of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.46,0:53:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of not holding up to the obligations that I've created to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.46,0:53:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to mow somebody's lawn for the next 30 years, and you feel guilty if you quit now?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.91,0:53:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a really good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.28,0:53:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're seeing yourself as indispensable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.02,0:53:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not indispensable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.34,0:53:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do a trade-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.48,0:53:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not indispensable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.60,0:53:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.76,0:53:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I closed up my private practice, I found other doctors that would take on the patients, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.34,0:53:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to stay in practice forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.56,0:53:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to stay in practice forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.74,0:53:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I found other doctors that would take them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.94,0:53:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.80,0:53:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.50,0:53:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.08,0:53:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.78,0:53:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can help them find another landscaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.82,0:53:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.08,0:53:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.31,0:53:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The camera's gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.29,0:53:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The battery's loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.45,0:53:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.48,0:54:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.01,0:54:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.50,0:54:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.12,0:54:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.48,0:54:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.73,0:54:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's rocks in this box.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.34,0:54:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.96,0:54:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's rocks in this box.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.46,0:54:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.90,0:54:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.70,0:54:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,oh they're hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.78,0:54:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,these are a gift from
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.88,0:54:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the boulder flock
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.60,0:54:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.52,0:54:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we have hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.72,0:54:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.90,0:54:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.80,0:54:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that's kind of a symbol of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.74,0:54:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,our enduring love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.23,0:54:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,very good
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.62,0:54:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.36,0:54:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,can you put peanut butter on one side
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.54,0:54:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and cream cheese on the other
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.10,0:55:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,peanut butter rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.50,0:55:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that's wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.57,0:55:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.31,0:55:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.88,0:55:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say I'm very grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.22,0:55:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.98,0:55:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very very much
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.37,0:55:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for being here
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.58,0:55:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.14,0:55:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.18,0:55:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,who I love very much
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.52,0:55:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and it aroused me
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.10,0:55:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,well this question several times
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.00,0:55:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.74,0:55:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.81,0:55:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that I know that next life
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.55,0:55:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.29,0:55:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,she loves what so much
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.52,0:55:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she loves the dog so much
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.70,0:55:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,oh you're a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.48,0:55:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.84,0:55:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is this possible that animals can attain
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.04,0:55:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this level of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.68,0:55:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,unconsciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.46,0:55:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or is only
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.46,0:55:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for humans
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.10,0:56:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or some beings
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.10,0:56:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.05,0:56:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,this is my question
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.05,0:56:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,can an animal obtain
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.98,0:56:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.98,0:56:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,potential
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.98,0:56:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a human
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.98,0:56:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.98,0:56:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it okay
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.14,0:56:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask this question
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.33,0:56:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,an animal's spirit can evolve
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.09,0:56:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,into eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.09,0:56:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,into a human spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.56,0:56:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it can evolve by getting reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.28,0:56:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in higher and higher realms
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.08,0:56:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,gets reborn in higher and higher realms
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.52,0:56:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,well thank you I'm very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.10,0:56:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for Domingo
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.10,0:56:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and for all the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.10,0:56:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and for all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.10,0:56:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
