Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.30,1:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.30,1:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,not karma
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.30,1:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,sins
