Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.69,1:14:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.69,1:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.69,1:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to give up, honey, because you have stopped killing animals already, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.05,1:14:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.97,1:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.45,1:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.09,1:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.67,1:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.91,1:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.33,1:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.67,1:14:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.06,1:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.25,1:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.29,1:14:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.27,1:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the first question is a friend of mine is wondering if there are any blocks or gates between level 540 and 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.39,1:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any major gates that I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.42,1:14:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there some?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.14,1:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The love becomes more and more unconditional, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.26,1:15:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the miraculous becomes more and more frequent.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.00,1:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.70,1:15:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.12,1:15:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the second question I'm asking for my mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.74,1:15:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm only supposed to ask one per person, but this is just for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.98,1:15:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's one each.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.71,1:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us live with a grandma that's committed to negativity.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.67,1:15:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.39,1:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And both of us are indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.91,1:15:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're interested in spiritual evolutions.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.19,1:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wondering how to not allow that to hinder us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.60,1:15:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she can't hinder you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.06,1:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But your response to her, what do you think it should be?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.98,1:15:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion to her innocence, my response should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.82,1:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she's innocent and ignorant, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.69,1:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's pretty much it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.35,1:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.59,1:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.27,1:15:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you try to be as compassionate and patient as you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.21,1:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A person like that who has no interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.51,1:16:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No interest in transcending their own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.07,1:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of learning how to live with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.56,1:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I always think the only way I can think of is by example.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.55,1:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But generally, people like that are immune to example too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.65,1:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be kind to you and you can be kind to them and they'll be just as bitchy as usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.08,1:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best, but thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.78,1:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.14,1:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't expect any change.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.04,1:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.53,1:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.61,1:16:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.35,1:16:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.81,1:16:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.25,1:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.97,1:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.67,1:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her to smoke marijuana.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.99,1:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That would help.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.71,1:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.08,1:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an old lady, 70 years old, and she grew marijuana.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.21,1:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She smoked a little marijuana every night before bed for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.97,1:17:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She grew it in the kitchen window.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.05,1:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, why do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.51,1:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, because I feel so relaxed and I just go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.99,1:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.99,1:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't take off her clothes and go dancing in the village square.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.97,1:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She just went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.90,1:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, the reason I and my husband and sister are here is because we needed your
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.32,1:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,aura patch, you might say, for our aura so that when we get to higher levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.92,1:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we can go through the high pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.48,1:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.80,1:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, when each level of consciousness has its own set of limitations that need to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.36,1:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,be transcended, are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.46,1:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.56,1:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.64,1:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.70,1:17:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.76,1:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.80,1:17:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.18,1:17:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.22,1:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That need to be transcended in the high 500s, 575, 585, are there limitations of perspective
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.38,1:18:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that need to be transcended?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.84,1:18:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that languaging is directly clinically correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.02,1:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In the high 500s, life becomes increasingly blissful and harmonious and eventually, eventually
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.31,1:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,constant joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.04,1:18:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the very highest 500s, you go into a state of ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.16,1:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it's very hard to function in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.08,1:18:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember in the high 500s, if you even looked at love, you couldn't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.56,1:18:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd just get overwhelmed with how profound it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.64,1:18:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you would find yourself weeping with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.22,1:18:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also noticed in certain...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.02,1:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In religious communities, what do you call them, communities?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.68,1:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloistered communities.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.68,1:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloistered, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.68,1:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a period where you cry all the time, it may last a couple of years, and any time
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.12,1:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you look at something, you can see the love and the beauty inherit.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.16,1:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it sort of melts into the 600 level, and the enlightenment level?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.18,1:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.18,1:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.18,1:19:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It just sort of melts and blends in.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.82,1:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a continuity, and of course, demarcating numbers is just an arbitrary, you know, what
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.42,1:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature out is it when you can say it's cold, you know, 26 degrees, 25 degrees, 24
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.68,1:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.68,1:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that exact, but the higher states of the 500s are increasingly joyful, and as
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.33,1:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember, actually ecstatic, and goes into a state of supreme ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.07,1:19:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.32,1:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.46,1:20:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God as profound joy and ecstasy, and you can't function in that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.32,1:20:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you sit on the porch swing all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.42,1:20:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.42,1:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sit on the porch swing all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.42,1:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sit on the porch swing all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.42,1:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.42,1:20:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't you bliss.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.42,1:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.74,1:20:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramakrishna went into that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.74,1:20:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember exactly that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.74,1:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.24,1:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.24,1:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.36,1:20:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.36,1:20:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.36,1:20:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.36,1:20:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.36,1:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.80,1:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.80,1:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.80,1:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
