Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.04,1:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.04,1:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.04,1:20:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.04,1:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for my wife who was supposed to be here today but she couldn't make it,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.48,1:20:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll read her question.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.76,1:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In May of 2007 my sister died of cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.88,1:20:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The evening she died, I was swimming, lapsed in the pool, and for a split second I had
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.88,1:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a feeling of extreme ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.74,1:21:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought my sister just got better, or she died.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.43,1:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, the next day, I found out that the feeling of ecstasy happened at the exact same
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.41,1:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,moment my sister died. Yes. Can you tell me the significance of that experience?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.47,1:21:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the relationship between the two people? They were siblings. Siblings, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.12,1:21:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Very close. Yes, well because of the alignment of consciousness she
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.56,1:21:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced the ecstasy as you enter heaven, yes. So was it her sister's soul
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.78,1:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way, saying goodbye or saying everything is fine? Her sister was
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.46,1:21:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,merely experiencing what you experience in that transition from physicality to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.73,1:21:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,heavenly. Because she was psychically attuned, she vicariously experienced it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.44,1:21:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like transmitted. It's like because of the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.97,1:22:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,identification between the two. Okay, so my wife's feeling was the same as her
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.89,1:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,sister's feeling at that moment? Yes, yes, yes. She picks up the vibration of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.39,1:22:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yeah. Thank you. Can I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.83,1:22:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because as you leave the body and enter that state there's a sense of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.18,1:22:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstasy. For one thing you've just left pain and suffering and you feel free and
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.38,1:22:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that you're reborn into a new realm. Yes. And it's the state is
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.31,1:22:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstatic. Okay, thank you. I remember in my own lifetime when my
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.82,1:22:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,mother left the body the state was ecstatic joy. Yeah. Hello Dr. Hawkins?
