Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.19,1:26:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where i would be without this work and um first of all i'm a spiritual student and i'm on a path
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.27,1:26:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and my intention is to release anything and
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.81,1:26:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.17,1:27:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,out of my life that is not serving me i'm a pathway to god and uh in the last year of work
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.67,1:27:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,i came up upon a stack a stack of what stack you know a stack a whole stack of people you want to
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.63,1:27:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,get rid of and not just people emotions and people and just emotions and people yeah and nothing i do
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.55,1:27:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to be able to shift it or no prayers i don't know this is how it seems to me and actually has
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.45,1:27:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to do with a relationship in my life that i think is integrous
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.75,1:27:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.17,1:27:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so my question is um what is the best way to release this
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.41,1:27:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the question how to release what this person yeah this person this person and the stack
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.22,1:27:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of you know everything that comes with it you know it's just with myself you want to dump somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.76,1:28:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,right i guess dump them dump them yeah okay somebody's shirt up here oh here his shirt
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.12,1:28:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody's shirt
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.26,1:28:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,i have a gift for you that's something that you had a great influence over so i just want to
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.54,1:28:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to give my deepest thanks and gratitude to you for the influence that you've had on my life and my
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.06,1:28:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,work yes and my question really isn't for me it's a request that you would continue the influence on
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.35,1:28:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that work and the people that it influences may i have your blessing for the people that
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.63,1:28:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,they choose to help in my work i don't get the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.83,1:29:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a person with Western
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.82,1:29:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,life
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.12,1:29:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah thank you for being my teacher um when the personal self disappears and the body is seen
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.80,1:29:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,separate from the self, and then the body moves around.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.10,1:29:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the self move?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.18,1:29:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the self doesn't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.63,1:29:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that which is aware of what's going on is here,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.49,1:29:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the body can be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.38,1:29:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is a shift where you can center in the body,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.54,1:29:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because you realize that's what the world thinks you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.78,1:29:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So for convenience, for convenience,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.64,1:29:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you can accommodate the world and humor it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.93,1:30:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so they think that you think you're the body, like they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.57,1:30:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a matter of choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.49,1:30:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.49,1:30:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When it first happens, you don't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.95,1:30:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is here, and your body's there,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.51,1:30:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody's talking to the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.09,1:30:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you wonder, who in the world are they talking to?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.29,1:30:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're here, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.95,1:30:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.66,1:30:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out of body, and they're talking
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.28,1:30:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the body, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.72,1:30:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world are they talking to?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.28,1:30:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll move it fast forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.69,1:30:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.53,1:30:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, what are your thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.53,1:30:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,on the presidency of Barack Obama so far?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.59,1:30:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any comments on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.29,1:30:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is what?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.01,1:30:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your thoughts on Barack Obama as president so far?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.25,1:30:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So far?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.63,1:30:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god, that's an evolving condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.59,1:30:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.37,1:30:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I watched FDR.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.69,1:30:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the history of FDR is very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.15,1:30:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,if you get that out and rerun it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.03,1:31:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see a lot of the same phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.13,1:31:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.03,1:31:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And because the role has multiple facets
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.70,1:31:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and multiple responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.04,1:31:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know, whether he's whatchamacallit
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.98,1:31:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that leads them over the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.02,1:31:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call that guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.91,1:31:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.39,1:31:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pied Piper.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.21,1:31:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pied Piper, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.21,1:31:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he's the Pied Piper, or whether he's
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.95,1:31:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the second coming, you know, you have
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.39,1:31:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.39,1:31:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Lima?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.39,1:31:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.71,1:31:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.71,1:31:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lima's also.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.71,1:31:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.71,1:31:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.71,1:31:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lima.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.71,1:31:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Lima that leads it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.71,1:31:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemmings.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.74,1:31:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemmings.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.74,1:31:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemmings into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.74,1:31:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.74,1:31:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemmings.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.74,1:31:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.74,1:31:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.74,1:31:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.74,1:31:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's a very difficult role he has
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.74,1:31:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.74,1:31:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.74,1:31:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you're going to fulfill that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.74,1:31:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,without all kinds of criticism from somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.74,1:31:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.74,1:31:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And a very difficult role that he has to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.74,1:31:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.74,1:31:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.74,1:31:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back home running for mayor in my city.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.74,1:32:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 12,000 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.74,1:32:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, would that be for the greater good of my community if I, a couple
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.74,1:32:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of years from now, running for mayor back home?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.74,1:32:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Would what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.74,1:32:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's for office?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.74,1:32:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Should he run for office?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.74,1:32:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.74,1:32:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.74,1:32:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.74,1:32:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.15,1:32:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the thing is to have integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.70,1:32:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be right all the time, and you can't be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.70,1:32:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can fulfill your role to the best of your ability, and that's all I hope any
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.76,1:32:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,president does is he fulfills the role to the best of his ability as he feels called
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.76,1:32:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,upon, and that's integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.76,1:32:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always figure if you realize that you're answerable to God for everything you do and
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.37,1:32:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,say, that's the only safeguard that the whole country has.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.37,1:32:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we have a president who feels he's answerable to divinity, then we're safeguarded by that,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.37,1:33:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,by that sense of righteousness and accountability.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.37,1:33:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So as long as a leader, I see that he realizes that he's accountable, accountable for honesty
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.37,1:33:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and integrity, then mistakes are inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.37,1:33:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.37,1:33:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, you know, you realize that the person did the best they could at the time knowing
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.37,1:33:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,what they knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.37,1:33:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they knew what they knew now, they wouldn't, you know, have voted that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.78,1:33:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're all crooks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.78,1:33:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's honest crooks.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.78,1:33:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's honest crooks and crooked crooks.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.31,1:33:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With the talk of these spiritual experiences earlier today, my question is about
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.31,1:33:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,an experience I had when I was 17, and I was at a camp, and they had, there was a minister
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.31,1:33:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,who said, if you want to accept Jesus as your Lord and Savior, I opened my eyes to the minister,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.38,1:33:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and it felt like one of those Monty Python movies where my head, like, split.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.41,1:34:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And this big, giant, gold beam of light poured out from wherever into my body and filled
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.44,1:34:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,every cell of my body with this golden white light.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.44,1:34:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it wasn't the same as what you guys had, but it was, you know, what, like, what was
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.14,1:34:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.17,1:34:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.17,1:34:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's a foolish question or not, but it's, but I hadn't…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.23,1:34:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.23,1:34:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's a divine energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.23,1:34:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He opened himself up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.23,1:34:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a divine energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.23,1:34:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He opened himself up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.23,1:34:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he a teacher of Jesus Christ?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.23,1:34:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.23,1:34:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.23,1:34:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the energy of Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.23,1:34:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you accept Christ as your Savior, you open the doorway for the radiance of that energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.23,1:34:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.10,1:34:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So then if we go about a normal, you know, then you kind of fall away and do your
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.40,1:34:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,own whatever normal…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.10,1:34:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those epiphanies are not continuous.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.10,1:34:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they call it an epiphany.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.10,1:34:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An epiphany is a high, high state like that, but you can't function in that state, so
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.10,1:35:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a state of illumination.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.10,1:35:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It changes you forever and your calibration changes, but you can't function in that state,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.10,1:35:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so it fades out because you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.10,1:35:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get used to the bright light, you're no longer blinded by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.14,1:35:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.14,1:35:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And we just stay on the path and keep reading and keep learning and keep praying and keep
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.14,1:35:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,releasing and keep…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.14,1:35:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.14,1:35:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.26,1:35:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just walk straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.26,1:35:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.26,1:35:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.74,1:35:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That condition is called an epiphany, a very high state of illumination.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.74,1:35:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Epiphany.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.12,1:35:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.54,1:35:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a spiritual path for a very long time, and I'm wondering if I hold this teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.54,1:35:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind, if you would calibrate him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.54,1:35:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.62,1:35:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.62,1:35:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to calibrate the teacher she's holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.98,1:35:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.98,1:35:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.52,1:35:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This teacher is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.52,1:36:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This teacher is not over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.26,1:36:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.70,1:36:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And may I have your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.73,1:36:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to give her my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.86,1:36:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.86,1:36:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.92,1:36:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.08,1:36:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.08,1:36:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we didn't mention any names.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.66,1:36:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.66,1:36:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.66,1:36:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it wasn't even when we knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.66,1:36:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want to know the name.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.66,1:36:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.54,1:36:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.54,1:36:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.54,1:36:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.66,1:36:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.66,1:36:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.59,1:36:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess a little premise.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.59,1:36:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to write this down.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.07,1:36:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.34,1:36:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Formulating a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.34,1:36:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.69,1:36:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.69,1:36:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.69,1:36:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.69,1:36:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.74,1:36:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.74,1:36:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.96,1:36:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.96,1:36:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.96,1:37:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.96,1:37:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.99,1:37:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.99,1:37:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done the best in two different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.99,1:37:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've formulated a million different ways, but my life is divergent right now where I
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.82,1:37:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,need to make a choice between self-evolution or social responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.44,1:37:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So-
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.44,1:37:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you see a conflict?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.08,1:37:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How are they different?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.26,1:37:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They just seem to be mutually exclusive to-
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.46,1:37:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.06,1:37:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you say on the spiritual growth, the spiritual path, surround yourself with like-minded
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.86,1:37:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.66,1:37:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,get on your way well that's an assist you don't need it you know you can get into lightning in a
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.22,1:37:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,cave all by yourself but fair enough that's that's a fair statement i guess my my ultimate
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.68,1:37:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,question was uh what in your words is uh your definition of integrity oh i can't really explain
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.75,1:38:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity to you just kind of like love just that undefinable you either know what it is you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.21,1:38:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if you climb a flagpole you're going to pick one with integrity and that one that wavers as you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.39,1:38:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,begin to climb on it right you're living your life and that puppy dog walks up to the door that sick
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.01,1:38:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,puppy dog that either can start taking care of that puppy or continue to live the rest of your
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.69,1:38:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,life what is that there's always that gray area there's no black and white there that's right
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.01,1:38:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no black and white but each choice influences your karmic consequences yes
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.07,1:38:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not either or
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.84,1:38:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.26,1:38:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because each one is really also an expression of the other it's like saying so i serve myself or
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.53,1:38:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,shall i serve the society you know there isn't any real ambiguity there because if you serve
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.16,1:39:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself by serving society a serving society you serve yourself so you know you can't create an
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.48,1:39:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,artificial dichotomy where there's none it's just a linguistic uh intellectual dichotomy in reality
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.22,1:39:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no dichotomy
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.74,1:39:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,dichotomy that's to serve your fellow man serve god and serve yourself all the same really well said
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.72,1:39:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you yeah was that the answer you wanted yeah i think it was your intention is that your
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.14,1:39:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,intention is but over power is everything else your intention is to save somebody and be a help
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.33,1:39:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to them and if they drown inadvertently in the process
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.45,1:39:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,well that's something different
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.69,1:39:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,okay you meant to you meant to give him the order to hang on to and accidentally hit him over the head
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.49,1:40:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and knocked him out with the order i mean and he and he drowned here's the order for the guys
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.53,1:40:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.66,1:40:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,hi can i shake your hand yes can i shake your hand yes
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.05,1:40:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so um i don't um my energy has been really bad the last couple months
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.74,1:40:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and i was wondering is it just that i need to change my antidepressant or
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.98,1:40:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what's okay what do you mean by your energy being bad i mean i just feel very low and tired you mean
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.30,1:40:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your emotions are feeling down yeah yeah okay yeah nothing wrong with your energy okay yeah yeah you're
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.82,1:40:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in a down yeah well take antidepressants do you do that yeah i do that but i'm wondering if the one
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.82,1:41:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,i've been taking for over a year if i should switch may change you need to change the dose you may
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.50,1:41:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,become immune to it change the dose or just ask for another one well i would try increasing the
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.50,1:41:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,dose with the doctor's permission and what else do you do to avoid depression you'll eat sugar and
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.68,1:41:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,sweets yes when are you going to quit them when my craving is done when my craving is done when my
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.58,1:41:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,craving is done when my craving is done you quit sugar and sweets your craving will disappear and
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.82,1:41:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so will your depression if i'm wrong i'll send you ten dollars if when you quit all sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.01,1:41:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you still go into these depressions then it requires a change in the medication dose
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.45,1:41:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but the kind of symptoms you get i would first stop sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.49,1:42:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then see what remains and then raise the dose if it's necessary but what about low
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.79,1:42:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,blood sugar? I just got through answering your question. Okay. If you spend more time listening
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.07,1:42:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and less time talking, you'd be better. Okay, thank you. Stop eating sugar and sweets. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.99,1:42:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you. And then see if you get better. Okay, thank you. If you don't get better,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.33,1:42:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go back to eating donuts and muffins. Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.49,1:42:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I pull your leg because I like you. She's coming a long way. Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.70,1:42:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit. The coffee toffee bars have caffeine, so if you need a jolt on the ride home.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.06,1:42:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. She has coffee toffee bars. Coffee toffee? Yeah, coffee toffee bars. Oh, oh, yes. Get the
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.06,1:42:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,hints. Get the hints. Yes, what else? May I have a blessing, please? Yes, indeed. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.44,1:43:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do have one question. And what? One question. What? She has one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.70,1:43:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're getting terrific feedback here. Yes. If you had permission to ask, could you
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.89,1:43:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me if it's in my highest good to move to Sedona? In the highest good to what? For her to
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.61,1:43:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,move to Sedona. Is it in the highest good? Oh, oh, I don't know. Do we have permission to ask this?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.20,1:43:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be in her highest good to move to Sedona. No. That would save you a lot of rent.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.15,1:43:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.49,1:43:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.76,1:43:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be not at this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.70,1:43:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it may be wrong timing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.54,1:43:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be, you know, at another time it might be on there, but at this time you get it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.16,1:43:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.74,1:43:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That could change now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.54,1:43:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because there's other things other than just the living. Where she's living, there's
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.22,1:43:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,relationships and opportunities and obligations, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.70,1:43:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.60,1:44:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just geographic.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.76,1:44:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.60,1:44:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.88,1:44:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold your hand, Susan?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.56,1:44:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.92,1:44:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.98,1:44:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.04,1:44:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.32,1:44:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I work as an acupuncturist at a substance abuse program, and we show your tapes, and
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.00,1:44:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I give them the map of consciousness, and I tell them that God is on the way up, and
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.62,1:44:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,recovery's on the way up, and addiction's on the way down, and they knew I was coming
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.04,1:44:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,here today, and I was wondering if we could say the serenity prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.04,1:44:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If what?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.06,1:44:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could say the serenity prayer together, all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.88,1:44:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.64,1:44:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.80,1:44:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the whole room?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.78,1:44:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.96,1:44:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.34,1:44:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.59,1:44:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.76,1:44:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.46,1:44:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.02,1:44:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.54,1:44:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.54,1:44:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.38,1:44:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.14,1:44:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Grant me the serenity to accept the things I cannot change, the courage to change the
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.30,1:44:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,things I can, and the wisdom to know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.68,1:44:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.10,1:45:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.76,1:45:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.62,1:45:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.42,1:45:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.68,1:45:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to watch the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.24,1:45:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.46,1:45:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to watch the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.67,1:45:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.67,1:45:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.49,1:45:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're past.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.49,1:45:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.93,1:45:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're past, but we can go on, because they said we could finish up real quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.85,1:45:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.77,1:45:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if you could give me your significance on an experience I had.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.61,1:45:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for like a split second, I convinced my mind that I was in a different body.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.13,1:45:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.83,1:45:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was like for a split second, and that happened twice, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.45,1:45:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering what...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.73,1:45:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrific.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.22,1:46:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Horrific?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.88,1:46:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.42,1:46:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach me how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.24,1:46:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.96,1:46:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.35,1:46:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I tried doing it with my cat another time, but it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.23,1:46:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By location.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.23,1:46:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just an interesting psychic.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.03,1:46:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a psychic phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.39,1:46:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A psychic.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.99,1:46:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's spiritual psychic.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.09,1:46:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.93,1:46:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.15,1:46:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No significance behind it?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.51,1:46:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.13,1:46:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harmless, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.21,1:46:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.61,1:46:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a blessing from both of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.07,1:46:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.37,1:46:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A double blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.85,1:46:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.97,1:46:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.59,1:46:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.03,1:46:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And God bless the innocence of your experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.86,1:46:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Dermot.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.06,1:46:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.33,1:46:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see very well at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.58,1:46:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sign things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.06,1:46:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.64,1:46:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.24,1:46:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jim, and this is Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.40,1:46:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Denver.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.30,1:47:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.76,1:47:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to relate a story to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.64,1:47:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.06,1:47:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.34,1:47:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And Jerry's going to relate a story to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.32,1:47:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.56,1:47:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your books have been life-changing for us, as well as those around us.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.90,1:47:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.06,1:47:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.28,1:47:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We met him at a coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.42,1:47:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim's been reading your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.50,1:47:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave him the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.76,1:47:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Versus Force.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.34,1:47:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Versus Force.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.20,1:47:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't read it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.04,1:47:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He flew on a plane to Manila.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.44,1:47:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes there for three months out of the year.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.08,1:47:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He read it on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.04,1:47:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He met a gentleman in Manila who is one of the chief negotiators for the Philippine government
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.84,1:47:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with Abu Sayyid.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.62,1:47:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.26,1:47:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He ordered five more copies and is going with the team, negotiating team, with the terrorists
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.72,1:47:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the southern part of the Philippines with your books as guides.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.76,1:47:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.76,1:47:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.76,1:47:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.76,1:47:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.46,1:48:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.82,1:48:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.82,1:48:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.82,1:48:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.82,1:48:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick question.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.82,1:48:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've often heard you say that there's no identity in enlightenment where you're sitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.48,1:48:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't an identity there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.38,1:48:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm curious as a student.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.02,1:48:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.02,1:48:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is an appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.02,1:48:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or useful way to relate to the persona of Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.02,1:48:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.44,1:48:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's transitory.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.44,1:48:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.44,1:48:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.82,1:49:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.08,1:49:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's also arbitrary.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.88,1:49:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I could also say the world needs another spiritual teacher like a hole in the head and quit it
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.88,1:49:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel no loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.88,1:49:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I could take the opposite view and say God blessed me with certain realizations.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.22,1:49:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That are helpful to share with others and feel an obligation.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.29,1:49:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason I became a teacher is I chose the latter.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.09,1:49:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That the gift was given to me and I didn't need to teach.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.09,1:49:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was by myself in a state of bliss, infinite bliss, beyond time, place, and location.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.37,1:49:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'd have to retrack again how that all came about.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.85,1:49:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The obligation of becoming a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.85,1:49:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to write power versus force.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.85,1:49:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.49,1:49:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because remember, we were discussing it and I said you need to write this down so someone
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.49,1:49:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,would.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.49,1:50:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she told me to write it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.49,1:50:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.45,1:50:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.45,1:50:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just kept it to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.45,1:50:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, gee, you really ought to share this and write it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.45,1:50:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.45,1:50:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.45,1:50:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.45,1:50:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.45,1:50:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we went back into the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.45,1:50:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.45,1:50:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we spent every weekend traveling.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.45,1:50:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent all our life in.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.45,1:50:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Planes.
