Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.63,1:50:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Charter, yeah, the Bill of Rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.03,1:50:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.91,1:51:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to calibrate the bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.23,1:51:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call it, Bill Charter of Rights?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.01,1:51:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Charter of Rights and Freedoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.31,1:51:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to calibrate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.56,1:51:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 480, 490, 495.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.24,1:51:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates at 495, over 495.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.52,1:51:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates at 495.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.32,1:51:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very high, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.50,1:51:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.42,1:51:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading it today, actually, and it doesn't mention God,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.30,1:51:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's probably one of the reasons why it doesn't calibrate high.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.12,1:51:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.12,1:51:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mention God, did it?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.84,1:51:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.28,1:51:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So that could be why it doesn't calibrate as high.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.34,1:51:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 500, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.84,1:51:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.69,1:51:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as well Canada stays away from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.11,1:51:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see all the trouble it brings you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.38,1:51:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to have a place to escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.54,1:51:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At least Canada, you can escape God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.64,1:51:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.66,1:51:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.36,1:51:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In my work in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.37,1:52:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an herbalist in the Oriental medical tradition.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.65,1:52:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.45,1:52:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And through reading your books,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.63,1:52:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been inspired to, as I'm with a patient,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.41,1:52:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,also just simply love them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.65,1:52:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.43,1:52:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.63,1:52:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,apart from simply generating that quality of love for who I'm with,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.97,1:52:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if you recommend a certain method like a visualization.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.65,1:52:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, I've recited the Medicine Buddha Mantra
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.81,1:52:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's part of my training.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.87,1:52:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.97,1:52:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.03,1:52:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.63,1:52:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
