Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.39,1:52:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.41,1:52:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.43,1:52:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.45,1:52:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.47,1:52:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.49,1:52:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.51,1:52:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had any advice for me
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.19,1:52:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to benefit my patients more through the love principle.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.77,1:52:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's just your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.03,1:52:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.99,1:52:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it came to the end of my practice, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.45,1:52:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the insurance cost more than I wasn't making enough to pay the insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.41,1:52:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't stop practice because there were a couple of guys
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.25,1:52:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that were hanging on really because of their relationship with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.25,1:52:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, geez, I can't desert these guys at this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.75,1:52:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they've come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.89,1:53:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And they've only got a half a mile left to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.83,1:53:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I figured I'll hang out with them until they leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.85,1:53:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When they leave, then I'll close my practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.88,1:53:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So when they left the body, I closed my practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.34,1:53:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was just caring about them to realize what you mean to them
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.38,1:53:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and to fulfill that meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.22,1:53:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if they were in psychoanalysis, it'd be different.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.28,1:53:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were in psychoanalysis, you would analyze out the positive transference.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.02,1:53:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, these people, the positive transference is what was keeping them going.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.28,1:53:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember one old guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.62,1:53:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, he was funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.52,1:53:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says, I want a picture of you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.62,1:53:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it on the wall because when I look at it, I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.24,1:53:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.82,1:53:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But he and his wife would fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.54,1:53:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And she wouldn't allow him to drive the car because he was too senile.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.87,1:54:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So he would go into a screaming fit that she wouldn't let him drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.79,1:54:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So one day, he got the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.05,1:54:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He took the keys to the car, and he drove, and he got lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.30,1:54:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And he called me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.12,1:54:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, tell your wife to come and get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.86,1:54:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.04,1:54:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, okay, Mildred, I get the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.69,1:54:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.58,1:54:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you care about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.92,1:54:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the caringness is transmitted, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.44,1:54:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The caringness, the energy of the caringness is carried over to the patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.30,1:54:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say, I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.52,1:54:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That would scare them.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.20,1:54:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But your caringness.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.58,1:54:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your power with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.64,1:54:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the healer is somebody who really cares about his patients.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.44,1:54:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He cares for their highest good, including preventing them from becoming
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.14,1:54:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,neurotically dependent on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.28,1:54:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So this old guy who felt better when he looked at my picture, because of his age,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.00,1:55:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to analyze that positive transference because it's keeping him alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.32,1:55:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was younger, I'd say, you know, you're projecting magic onto me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.66,1:55:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your will to get better and your will to live that's energizing,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.38,1:55:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you're functioning, not me, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.94,1:55:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.96,1:55:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.16,1:55:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on the patient, the relationship, the phase,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.30,1:55:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and what it is you're trying to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.25,1:55:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.09,1:55:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.41,1:55:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you also, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.90,1:55:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.38,1:55:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't hurt to pray for a patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.24,1:55:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to pray for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.60,1:55:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, God, if you don't mind it, I hope Mac gets better.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.76,1:55:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.32,1:55:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to bother God with all kinds of stuff, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.47,1:55:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.31,1:55:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.13,1:55:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.19,1:55:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to look into your eyes and experience you closer than back there in the back of the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.55,1:55:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.49,1:56:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a question about something that happened to me quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.29,1:56:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.35,1:56:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was probably about 25 or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.49,1:56:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I started going to a meditation class, and they talked about love.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.07,1:56:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, well, I don't know what that feels like.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.61,1:56:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I meditated on love every day for about a year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.95,1:56:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.07,1:56:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But what happened was, all of a sudden, I was leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.79,1:56:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, life was shit, but all of a sudden, I felt what love felt like, and I was leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.69,1:56:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is what it feels like, I'm going to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.21,1:56:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.73,1:56:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my life just rolled in front of me, and I realized that wasn't a failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.59,1:56:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.03,1:56:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.21,1:56:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I'd done was a total success, and that's the only way it could have ever been.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.09,1:56:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.78,1:56:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Recontextualize the whole thing, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.84,1:57:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to come back because I had more to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.64,1:57:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.90,1:57:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, what did that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.51,1:57:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did that go?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.81,1:57:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something way past that in consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.57,1:57:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Way past what?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.17,1:57:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.83,1:57:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.73,1:57:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the ultimate love resolves all differentiation of a this from a that, or a me and a you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.77,1:57:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it merges into, what's the right word for it, of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.45,1:57:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It merges into divinity in which there is no me and you, or this and a that.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.83,1:57:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unity.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.73,1:57:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.47,1:58:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for all your writings, and your map is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.94,1:58:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.40,1:58:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.88,1:58:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time we got left?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.00,1:58:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We better, I better watch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.04,1:58:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're all done.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.94,1:58:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're over.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.98,1:58:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're over the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.72,1:58:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now, doctor's going to shake everyone's hand in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.60,1:58:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
