Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.50,1:58:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you could come down the center aisles and come across the front of the stage, he'll be over here, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.42,1:58:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that where he's going to be?
